T06:06:30.304914+00:00\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/run-log.md b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex f2cc90f..abd9e13 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- a/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -123,3 +123,6 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-032@20260416t181925z-1776402371 | T-032@20260416T181925Z | claude | gemini | PASS | 356.1s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-033@20260416t181925z-1776402750 | T-033@20260416T181925Z | codex | claude | PASS | 505.6s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-034@20260416t181925z-1776403274 | T-034@20260416T181925Z | claude | gemini | PASS | 366.5s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-035@20260416t181925z-1776403664 | T-035@20260416T181925Z | codex | claude | PASS | 1083.4s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-036@20260416t181925z-1776404764 | T-036@20260416T181925Z | claude | gemini | PASS | 543.0s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-037@20260416t181925z-1776405323 | T-037@20260416T181925Z | codex | claude | PASS | 648.0s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/specs/t-038@20260416t181925z-spec.md b/specs/t-038@20260416t181925z-spec.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nnew file mode 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex 0000000..4cfa2cb\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- /dev/null\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/specs/t-038@20260416t181925z-spec.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -0,0 +1,115 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+# Specification: T-038@20260416T181925Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Problem Statement\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+`compose_score_tree()` creates `SectionNode` instances with default-constructed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+`SectionEnvelope()` — all parameters at flat defaults. The procedural arc system\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+already computes rich per-section metadata (density, dynamic, harmonic target,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+spatial intent, synthesis type) via `ArcDirective`, and the piece brief carries\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+narrative state (arc_phase, mood, creative_energy, curiosity). None of this\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+narrative context currently flows into the section envelope, so tension\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+trajectories, brightness curves, and density targets are disconnected from the\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+dramatic arc.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+This task couples the narrative engine (procedural arc + piece brief narrative\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+state) to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Technical Approach\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+### New module: `src/cypherclaw/render/narrative_envelope.py`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+1. Define `ToneVector` (frozen dataclass):\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `darkness`: float [0.0, 1.0] — maps from mood (negative mood → higher darkness)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `energy`: float [0.0, 1.0] — maps from creative_energy\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `warmth`: float [0.0, 1.0] — derived from timbre target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `density`: float [0.0, 1.0] — from arc directive density_target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+2. Define `NarrativeBeat` (frozen dataclass):\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `arc_phase`: str — phase name (Divination/Emergence/Conversation/Convergence/Crystallization)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `section_function`: str — from form grammar (invocation/statement/development/turn/recap/coda/etc.)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `tension_target`: float [0.0, 1.0] — overall tension level for this beat\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - `tone`: ToneVector — tone dimensions for this beat\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+3. Implement `envelope_for_beat(beat: NarrativeBeat) -> SectionEnvelope`:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - **tension_trajectory**: breakpoint function shaped by arc_phase (each phase\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+     has a characteristic shape: Divination rises slowly, Conversation sustains\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+     high, Crystallization settles). Section function modifies the shape\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+     (development/turn push the peak, recap/coda pull toward resolution).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - **density_target**: scalar from `tone.density`, clamped to [0.05, 0.95].\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - **dynamic_plane**: derived from `tone.energy` with `tone.darkness` influence.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+     Higher energy → higher dynamic plane; higher darkness → slight reduction.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - **brightness**: derived from `1.0 - tone.darkness` with energy boost.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - **tempo_base**: scaled from a base of 1.0, modified by arc phase energy\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+     (Conversation faster, Crystallization slower).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+4. Implement `tone_from_narrative(*, arc_phase, mood, creative_energy, curiosity,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   density_target, dynamic_target, timbre_target) -> ToneVector`:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - Converts raw narrative state into a normalized ToneVector.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+5. Implement `beat_from_directive(directive, section_function) -> NarrativeBeat`:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   - Convenience factory that builds a NarrativeBeat from an ArcDirective +\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+     section function string.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+### Integration in `recursive_composer.py`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+6. Replace `SectionEnvelope()` on line 235 with:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   ```python\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   section_envelope=envelope_for_beat(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+       beat_from_directive(directive, section.function)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   ```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   where `directive` is the per-section ArcDirective already computed in\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   `_production_arc_for_sections()`. Refactor to return directives alongside\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   metadata so they're available during section construction.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Edge Cases\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- Missing arc directive (commission.arc_directive is None): fall back to\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  Emergence-phase defaults for the tone vector.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- Unknown arc phase name: treat as Emergence (the middle-ground phase).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- Unknown section function: use neutral tension modifiers (no boost or reduction).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- All parameters must remain within their validated ranges after scaling.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Assumptions\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- The \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"existing narrative engine interface\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" is the procedural arc system\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  (ArcDirective, ArcPhase, directive_for_elapsed) since the full narrative\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  engine from the PRD is not yet built.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- The ToneVector here is a lightweight musical-facing tone representation,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  not the full 8-dimension NE-009 ToneController — that will be built when\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  the narrative engine PRD is implemented. This module is designed to be\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  replaced/extended by the full tone controller later.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- No new external dependencies are required.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- The candidate hardening items referencing bootstrap_identity,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  FirstBootAnnouncer, budget enforcement, and revise_score integration are\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  out of scope for this task (narrative envelope coupling has no interaction\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+  with startup sequencing, resource budgets, or the self-critique pipeline).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Acceptance Criteria\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+1. Each procedural arc phase produces a distinct tension_trajectory shape with\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   characteristic breakpoints (Divination: rising slowly; Conversation: sustained\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   high; Crystallization: settling).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_narrative_envelope.py::TestEnvelopeForBeat::test_arc_phase_produces_distinct_tension_shapes -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+2. Section function modifies the base tension shape (development/turn push peaks\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   higher; recap/coda pull toward resolution).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_narrative_envelope.py::TestEnvelopeForBeat::test_section_function_modifies_tension -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+3. ToneVector (darkness, energy, warmth, density) influences brightness,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   dynamic_plane, and density_target in the resulting envelope.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_narrative_envelope.py::TestEnvelopeForBeat::test_tone_vector_influences_envelope_parameters -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+4. beat_from_directive correctly converts an ArcDirective into a NarrativeBeat\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   with appropriate tone vector values.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_narrative_envelope.py::TestBeatFromDirective::test_directive_to_beat_conversion -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+5. Determinism: identical inputs produce byte-identical SectionEnvelope instances.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_narrative_envelope.py::TestEnvelopeForBeat::test_deterministic_output -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+6. compose_score_tree() populates non-default section envelopes on every section\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   node, with tension_trajectory driven by the procedural arc.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_narrative_envelope.py::TestComposerIntegration::test_score_tree_sections_have_narrative_envelopes -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+7. All existing tests continue to pass (no regressions).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/ -x -q`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/src/cypherclaw/render/narrative_envelope.py b/src/cypherclaw/render/narrative_envelope.py\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nnew file mode 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex 0000000..820edc3\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- /dev/null\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/src/cypherclaw/render/narrative_envelope.py\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -0,0 +1,172 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Narrative beat to SectionEnvelope coupling.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+Maps procedural arc state (phase, density, dynamic, timbre) and section\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+function into populated SectionEnvelope instances so dramatic arcs drive\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+section-level musical parameters.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from __future__ import annotations\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from dataclasses import dataclass\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from .events import Breakpoint, SectionEnvelope\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+@dataclass(frozen=True)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+class ToneVector:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    darkness: float = 0.5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    energy: float = 0.5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    warmth: float = 0.5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    density: float = 0.5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+@dataclass(frozen=True)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+class NarrativeBeat:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    arc_phase: str\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    section_function: str\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tension_target: float\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tone: ToneVector\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+_DYNAMIC_ENERGY: dict[str, float] = {\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"pp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.12,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"p\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.25,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"mp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.42,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"mf\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.58,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"f\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.78,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ff\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.92,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+_TIMBRE_WARMTH: dict[str, float] = {\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sparse\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.2,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"warm\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.65,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"complex\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"bright\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.35,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"pure\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.7,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+_PHASE_TENSION_SHAPES: dict[str, tuple[Breakpoint, ...]] = {\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": ((0.0, 0.08), (0.5, 0.15), (1.0, 0.25)),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": ((0.0, 0.18), (0.5, 0.35), (1.0, 0.50)),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": ((0.0, 0.50), (0.3, 0.65), (0.7, 0.72), (1.0, 0.60)),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Convergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": ((0.0, 0.60), (0.35, 0.85), (0.7, 0.65), (1.0, 0.45)),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": ((0.0, 0.35), (0.3, 0.22), (0.7, 0.12), (1.0, 0.06)),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+_FUNCTION_TENSION_MODIFIER: dict[str, tuple[float, float]] = {\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"invocation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (-0.05, 0.0),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"statement\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.0, 0.0),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"arrival\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.05, 0.05),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"lift\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.05, 0.08),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"development\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.08, 0.12),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"turn\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.10, 0.15),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"contrast\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.06, 0.10),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"bridge\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (-0.02, -0.15),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"release\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (-0.05, -0.25),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recap\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.10, -0.38),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"resolution\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.05, -0.40),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"coda\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (0.08, -0.42),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"residue\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": (-0.02, -0.40),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+_PHASE_TEMPO_SCALE: dict[str, float] = {\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.92,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.97,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 1.05,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Convergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 1.02,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": 0.88,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def _clamp(value: float, lo: float = 0.0, hi: float = 1.0) -> float:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return max(lo, min(hi, value))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def _modify_breakpoints(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    base: tuple[Breakpoint, ...],\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    start_offset: float,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    end_offset: float,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+) -> tuple[Breakpoint, ...]:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    n = len(base)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    result: list[Breakpoint] = []\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    for i, (pos, val) in enumerate(base):\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        t = i / max(1, n - 1)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        offset = start_offset + (end_offset - start_offset) * t\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        result.append((pos, _clamp(val + offset)))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return tuple(result)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def envelope_for_beat(beat: NarrativeBeat) -> SectionEnvelope:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    phase = beat.arc_phase\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    if phase not in _PHASE_TENSION_SHAPES:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        phase = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    func = beat.section_function\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    start_mod, end_mod = _FUNCTION_TENSION_MODIFIER.get(func, (0.0, 0.0))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tension_base = _PHASE_TENSION_SHAPES[phase]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tension_points = _modify_breakpoints(tension_base, start_mod, end_mod)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    density = _clamp(beat.tone.density, 0.05, 0.95)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    brightness = _clamp((1.0 - beat.tone.darkness) * 0.7 + beat.tone.energy * 0.3)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    dynamic = _clamp(beat.tone.energy * 0.7 + (1.0 - beat.tone.darkness) * 0.2 + beat.tone.warmth * 0.1)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tempo = max(0.5, _PHASE_TEMPO_SCALE.get(phase, 1.0))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return SectionEnvelope(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        tempo_base=tempo,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        density_target=density,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dynamic_plane=dynamic,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        brightness=brightness,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        tension_trajectory=tension_points,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def tone_from_narrative(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    *,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    arc_phase: str,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    mood: float,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    creative_energy: float,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    curiosity: float,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    density_target: float,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    dynamic_target: str,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    timbre_target: str,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+) -> ToneVector:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    darkness = _clamp(0.5 - mood * 0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    energy_base = _DYNAMIC_ENERGY.get(dynamic_target, 0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    energy = _clamp(creative_energy * 0.6 + energy_base * 0.4)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    warmth = _TIMBRE_WARMTH.get(timbre_target, 0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    density = _clamp(density_target)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return ToneVector(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        darkness=darkness,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        energy=energy,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        warmth=warmth,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        density=density,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def beat_from_directive(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    directive: object,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    section_function: str,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+) -> NarrativeBeat:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    phase_name = getattr(getattr(directive, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"phase\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", None), \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    density = float(getattr(directive, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"density_target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", 0.5) or 0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    dynamic = str(getattr(directive, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"dynamic_target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"mf\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\") or \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"mf\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    timbre = str(getattr(directive, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timbre_target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"warm\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\") or \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"warm\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    compression = float(getattr(directive, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"compression_target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", 0.3) or 0.3)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tone = tone_from_narrative(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        arc_phase=phase_name,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        mood=0.0,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        creative_energy=_clamp(1.0 - compression),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        curiosity=0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        density_target=density,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dynamic_target=dynamic,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        timbre_target=timbre,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tension_base = _clamp(density * 0.6 + _DYNAMIC_ENERGY.get(dynamic, 0.5) * 0.4)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return NarrativeBeat(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        arc_phase=phase_name,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        section_function=section_function,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        tension_target=tension_base,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        tone=tone,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/tests/test_narrative_envelope.py b/tests/test_narrative_envelope.py\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nnew file mode 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex 0000000..a77e6d1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- /dev/null\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/tests/test_narrative_envelope.py\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -0,0 +1,466 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Tests for narrative beat → SectionEnvelope coupling (T-038).\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from __future__ import annotations\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+import math\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+import os\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+import sys\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sys.path.insert(0, os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"..\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"my-claw\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tools\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sys.path.insert(0, os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"..\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"my-claw\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tools\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"senseweave\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from cypherclaw.render.narrative_envelope import (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    NarrativeBeat,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    ToneVector,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    beat_from_directive,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    envelope_for_beat,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tone_from_narrative,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from cypherclaw.render.events import SectionEnvelope\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+from senseweave.procedural_arc import ARC_PHASES, ArcDirective, directive_for_elapsed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def _sample_tension_at(envelope: SectionEnvelope, position: float) -> float:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return envelope.value_at(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tension_trajectory\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", position)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+def _make_beat(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    arc_phase: str = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    section_function: str = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"statement\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    tension_target: float = 0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    darkness: float = 0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    energy: float = 0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    warmth: float = 0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    density: float = 0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+) -> NarrativeBeat:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    return NarrativeBeat(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        arc_phase=arc_phase,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        section_function=section_function,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        tension_target=tension_target,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        tone=ToneVector(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            darkness=darkness,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            energy=energy,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            warmth=warmth,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            density=density,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        ),\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+class TestEnvelopeForBeat:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    def test_arc_phase_produces_distinct_tension_shapes(self) -> None:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        phases = [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Convergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        envelopes = {\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            phase: envelope_for_beat(_make_beat(arc_phase=phase))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            for phase in phases\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        }\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        div_start = _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], 0.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        div_end = _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], 1.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert div_end > div_start, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination should rise\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        conv_mid = _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], 0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert conv_mid >= 0.55, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation mid should be high tension\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        cryst_start = _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], 0.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        cryst_end = _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], 1.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert cryst_end < cryst_start, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization should settle\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        emerg_end = _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], 1.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert emerg_end > div_end * 0.8, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence should rise higher than Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        conv_peak = max(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Convergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], p)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            for p in [0.0, 0.25, 0.35, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        cryst_peak = max(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            _sample_tension_at(envelopes[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"], p)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            for p in [0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert conv_peak > cryst_peak, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Convergence peak should exceed Crystallization peak\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    def test_section_function_modifies_tension(self) -> None:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        base = envelope_for_beat(_make_beat(section_function=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"statement\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dev = envelope_for_beat(_make_beat(section_function=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"development\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        turn = envelope_for_beat(_make_beat(section_function=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"turn\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        recap = envelope_for_beat(_make_beat(section_function=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recap\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        coda = envelope_for_beat(_make_beat(section_function=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"coda\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        base_peak = max(_sample_tension_at(base, p) for p in [0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0])\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dev_peak = max(_sample_tension_at(dev, p) for p in [0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0])\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        turn_peak = max(_sample_tension_at(turn, p) for p in [0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0])\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        recap_end = _sample_tension_at(recap, 1.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        coda_end = _sample_tension_at(coda, 1.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert dev_peak > base_peak, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"development should push peak higher\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert turn_peak > base_peak, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"turn should push peak higher\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert recap_end < _sample_tension_at(recap, 0.0), \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recap should resolve toward end\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert coda_end < _sample_tension_at(coda, 0.0), \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"coda should resolve toward end\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    def test_tone_vector_influences_envelope_parameters(self) -> None:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        bright_beat = _make_beat(darkness=0.1, energy=0.8)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dark_beat = _make_beat(darkness=0.9, energy=0.2)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        bright_env = envelope_for_beat(bright_beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dark_env = envelope_for_beat(dark_beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        bright_sample = bright_env.sample(0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dark_sample = dark_env.sample(0.5)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert bright_sample.brightness > dark_sample.brightness, (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"low darkness should produce higher brightness\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert bright_sample.dynamic_plane > dark_sample.dynamic_plane, (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"high energy should produce higher dynamic plane\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dense_beat = _make_beat(density=0.9)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        sparse_beat = _make_beat(density=0.1)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        dense_env = envelope_for_beat(dense_beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        sparse_env = envelope_for_beat(sparse_beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        assert dense_env.sample(0.5).density_target > sparse_env.sample(0.5).density_target, (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"higher tone density should produce higher density_target\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    def test_deterministic_output(self) -> None:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        beat = _make_beat(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            arc_phase=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            section_function=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"development\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            tension_target=0.7,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            darkness=0.3,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            energy=0.6,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            warmth=0.5,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            density=0.65,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        )\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        env_a = envelope_for_beat(beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        env_b = envelope_for_beat(beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        for position in [0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0]:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            sample_a = env_a.sample(position)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            sample_b = env_b.sample(position)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            assert sample_a == sample_b, f\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Envelopes differ at position {position}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+    def test_all_parameters_in_valid_range(self) -> None:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        phases = [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Divination\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Emergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Conversation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Convergence\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Crystallization\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        functions = [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"invocation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"statement\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"development\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"turn\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recap\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"coda\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"residue\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+        for phase in phases:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+            for func in functions:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+                beat = _make_beat(arc_phase=phase, section_function=func)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+                env = envelope_for_beat(beat)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+                for pos in [0.0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0]:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+                    sample = env.sample(pos)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+                    assert sample.tempo_base > 0.0, f\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tempo_base must be > 0 at {phase}/{func}/{pos}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+                    assert 0.0 <= sample.density_target <= 1.0, f\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"density_target out of range at {phase}/{func}/{pos}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\