sdp/verification/t-012@20260416t181925z-verify.md:19:The task is complete. The scheduler (`schedule_scene` and `schedule_song`) now supports an optional `sensor_fn` to provide real-time modulation and a `delta_track_path` to persist these values. A `replay_sensor_fn` is provided to enable deterministic replay from the persisted delta track, satisfying the requirement for replay capability.
sdp/verification/t-012@20260416t181925z-verify.md:36:The core scheduler implementation for the delta track is robust and well-tested. The capability to record and replay expressive modulations is now fully integrated into the `music_tracker_runtime`. Future tasks (like T-037) can now utilize the `delta_track_path` and `replay_sensor_fn` for full performance reproduction.
