+| Model pattern | Input price per 1M tokens | Output price per 1M tokens |
+| --- | ---: | ---: |
+| claude-opus-4 | $15.00 | $75.00 |
+| claude-sonnet-4 | $3.00 | $15.00 |
+| claude-haiku | $0.80 | $4.00 |
+| gpt-4o | $2.50 | $10.00 |
+| o3 | $10.00 | $40.00 |
+| codex-mini | $1.50 | $6.00 |
+| fallback | $3.00 | $15.00 |
